See the LICENSE files for details.

The license covers all source files in the ATK distribution, with the
exception of the following third party software parts, which remain licensed
under their respective licenses.

Third party software
====================
ATK uses the Smarty template engine by Ispi. The Smarty template engine 
(http://smarty.php.net) is Copyright (c) 2001-2003 Ispi and made available
under the Library General Public License (LGPL).

ATK uses the DHTML Calendar Widget by Mihai Bazon. The DHTML Calendar Widget
(http://dynarch.com/mishoo/calendar.epl) is Copyright (c) 2002-2004 Mihai
Bazon and made available under the Library General Public License (LGPL). 

ATK uses modified versions of PHPLIB's database abstraction classes for
database access. PHPLIB (http://phplib.netuse.de) is Copyright (c) 1998,1999 
SH Online Dienst GmbH and made available under the Library General Public 
License (LGPL). 

ATK uses functions from the ADOdb Date Library, for date support prior to
1970. The ADOdb Date Library (http://php.weblogs.com/adodb_date_time_library)
is Copyright (c) 2003 John Lim and maide available under a BSD-style license.

ATK uses SimpleTest (http://www.lastcraft.com/simple_test.php) for unit 
testing. SimpleTest is Copyright (c)2003-2005 Marcus Baker (lastcraft.com) and
made available under the Open Group Test Suite License. The full version of 
SimpleTest including full documentation can be found on its homepage. Included 
with permission.

ATK uses the FCKEditor (http://www.fckeditor.net) for wysiwyg editing.
fckEditor is Copyright (c)2003-2005 Frederico Caldeira Knabben and made 
available under the LGPL license. The full version of fckEditor including full
documentation can be found on its homepage.

ATK uses TinyButStrong OOo (http://www.tinybutstrong.com/apps/tbsooo/)
for parsing OpenOffice.org and OpenDocument template files. TinyButStrong
OOo is Copyright (c) 2005 Olivier LOYNET and released under the GNU Lesser
General Public License (LGPL). The full version including examples
and documentation can be downloaded from its homepage.